}}'''2020年美国联邦政府数据泄露事件'''是指在2020年，一个由他国政府支持的组织发动了一场大规模网络攻击。<ref name="nyt-2020-12-14">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/14/us/politics/russia-hack-nsa-homeland-security-pentagon.html|title=Scope of Russian Hack Becomes Clear: Multiple U.S. Agencies Were Hit|first=David E.|author=Sanger|first2=Nicole|author2=Perlroth|first3=Eric|last3=Schmitt|date=December 15, 2020|work=The New York Times|accessdate=December 15, 2020|archivedate=December 18, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062201/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/14/us/politics/russia-hack-nsa-homeland-security-pentagon.html}}</ref><ref name="bbc-2020-12-19">{{Cite web|title=US cyber-attack: Russia 'clearly' behind SolarWinds operation, says Pompeo|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-55374945|accessdate=2020-12-19|date=2020-12-19|publisher=BBC|archive-date=2021-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527220606/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-55374945|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Washington|first=Georgi Kantchev in Moscow and Warren P. Strobel in|date=2021-01-02|title=How Russia's 'Info Warrior' Hackers Let Kremlin Play Geopolitics on the Cheap|language=en-US|work=Wall Street Journal|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/how-russias-info-warrior-hackers-let-kremlin-play-geopolitics-on-the-cheap-11609592401|accessdate=2021-01-05|issn=0099-9660|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108150801/https://www.wsj.com/articles/how-russias-info-warrior-hackers-let-kremlin-play-geopolitics-on-the-cheap-11609592401|dead-url=no}}</ref>全球包括美国各级政府部门、[[北约|北约]]、[[英國政府|英国政府]]、[[欧洲议会|欧洲议会]]、[[微软|微软]]等至少200个政府单位、组织或公司受到影响，其中一些组织的数据可能也遭到了泄露。<ref name="bloomberg-2020-12-14">{{Cite web|title=U.K. Government, NATO Join U.S. in Monitoring Risk From Hack|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-14/u-k-government-nato-join-u-s-in-monitoring-risk-from-hack|accessdate=December 16, 2020|date=December 14, 2020|publisher=Bloomberg L.P.|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215021953/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-14/u-k-government-nato-join-u-s-in-monitoring-risk-from-hack|archivedate=December 15, 2020}}</ref><ref name="bloomberg-2020-12-19-200">{{Cite web|title=At Least 200 Victims Identified in Suspected Russian Hacking|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-19/at-least-200-victims-identified-in-suspected-russian-hacking|date=December 19, 2020|access-date=2021-03-03|archive-date=2021-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210406063950/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-19/at-least-200-victims-identified-in-suspected-russian-hacking|dead-url=no}}</ref>由于此次网络攻击和数据泄露事件持续时间久，目标知名度高、敏感性强，多家媒体将其列为美国遭受过的最严重的网络安全事件。

此次攻击在2020年12月13日首次公开报道前已经持续数月，最初披露的报告列明的受影响组织仅包括[[美国财政部|美国财政部]]和[[美国商务部|美国商务部]]下属的国家电信和信息管理局（NTIA）。随后，更多单位发现其数据遭到泄露。<ref name="reuters-initial">{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/usa-cyber-treasury-idUSL1N2IT0I8|title=REFILE-EXCLUSIVE-U.S. Treasury breached by hackers backed by foreign government – sources|first=Christopher|author=Bing|date=December 13, 2020|work=Reuters|accessdate=December 14, 2020|archivedate=December 14, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214024713/https://www.reuters.com/article/usa-cyber-treasury-idUSL1N2IT0I8}}</ref><ref name="wapo">{{Cite web|title=Russian government spies are behind a broad hacking campaign that has breached U.S. agencies and a top cyber firm|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/russian-government-spies-are-behind-a-broad-hacking-campaign-that-has-breached-us-agencies-and-a-top-cyber-firm/2020/12/13/d5a53b88-3d7d-11eb-9453-fc36ba051781_story.html|accessdate=December 14, 2020|author=Nakashima|date=December 13, 2020|first=Ellen|work=The Washington Post|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213220635/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/russian-government-spies-are-behind-a-broad-hacking-campaign-that-has-breached-us-agencies-and-a-top-cyber-firm/2020/12/13/d5a53b88-3d7d-11eb-9453-fc36ba051781_story.html|archivedate=December 13, 2020}}</ref><ref name="nyt-2020-12-14">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/14/us/politics/russia-hack-nsa-homeland-security-pentagon.html|title=Scope of Russian Hack Becomes Clear: Multiple U.S. Agencies Were Hit|first=David E.|author=Sanger|first2=Nicole|author2=Perlroth|first3=Eric|last3=Schmitt|date=December 15, 2020|work=The New York Times|accessdate=December 15, 2020|archivedate=December 18, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062201/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/14/us/politics/russia-hack-nsa-homeland-security-pentagon.html}}</ref><ref name="reuters-2020-12-14">{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/global-cyber-idUSKBN28O1Z3|title=U.S. Homeland Security, thousands of businesses scramble after suspected Russian hack|first=Jack|author=Stubbs|first2=Raphael|author2=Satter|first3=Joseph|last3=Menn|date=December 15, 2020|work=Reuters|accessdate=December 15, 2020|archivedate=December 15, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215113854/https://www.reuters.com/article/global-cyber-idUSKBN28O1Z3}}</ref><ref name="bloomberg-2020-12-14">{{Cite web|title=U.K. Government, NATO Join U.S. in Monitoring Risk From Hack|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-14/u-k-government-nato-join-u-s-in-monitoring-risk-from-hack|accessdate=December 16, 2020|date=December 14, 2020|publisher=Bloomberg L.P.|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215021953/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-14/u-k-government-nato-join-u-s-in-monitoring-risk-from-hack|archivedate=December 15, 2020}}</ref>

此次网络攻击事件最晚开始于2020年3月<ref name="reuters_2020-12-14_by_bing">{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-cyber-treasury-exclsuive-idUSKBN28N0PG|title=Suspected Russian hackers spied on U.S. Treasury emails – sources|first=Christopher|author=Bing|date=December 14, 2020|work=Reuters|accessdate=December 14, 2020|archivedate=December 14, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214025738/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-cyber-treasury-exclsuive-idUSKBN28N0PG}}</ref><ref name="chron">{{Cite web|title=EXPLAINER: How bad is the hack that targeted US agencies?|url=https://www.chron.com/news/article/Explainer-How-bad-is-the-hack-that-targeted-US-15800740.php|accessdate=December 15, 2020|author=O'Brien|date=December 15, 2020|first=Matt|work=Houston Chronicle|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214232009/https://www.chron.com/news/article/Explainer-How-bad-is-the-hack-that-targeted-US-15800740.php|archivedate=December 14, 2020}}</ref>，期间，攻击者至少利用了微软、[[SolarWinds|SolarWinds]]和[[VMware|VMware]]三家企业的软件或凭证。<ref name="reuters-2020-12-17-ms">{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-usa-cyber-breach-idUKKBN28R3B7|title=Microsoft says it found malicious software in its systems|first=Joseph|author=Menn|date=December 18, 2020|work=Reuters|accessdate=December 17, 2020|archivedate=December 18, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062143/https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-usa-cyber-breach-idUKKBN28R3B7}}</ref><ref name="krebs-2020-12-18">{{Cite web|title=VMware Flaw a Vector in SolarWinds Breach?|url=https://krebsonsecurity.com/2020/12/vmware-flaw-a-vector-in-solarwinds-breach/|accessdate=December 18, 2020|date=December 7, 2020|publisher=[[Krebs_on_Security|Krebs on Security]]|archive-date=2021-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210311213646/https://krebsonsecurity.com/2020/12/vmware-flaw-a-vector-in-solarwinds-breach/|dead-url=no}}</ref>攻击者通过对微软云服务实施供应链攻击获得入侵微软云服务客户的能力<ref name="wapo-2020-12-24">{{Cite web|title=Russian hackers compromised Microsoft cloud customers through third party, putting emails and other data at risk|url=https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/us/russian-hackers-compromised-microsoft-cloud-customers-through-third-party-putting-emails-and-other-data-at-risk/ar-BB1cdqp0|work=www.msn.com|access-date=2021-03-03|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417062159/https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/us/russian-hackers-compromised-microsoft-cloud-customers-through-third-party-putting-emails-and-other-data-at-risk/ar-BB1cdqp0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="reuters-2020-12-24">{{Cite web|title=Suspected Russian hackers used Microsoft vendors to breach customers|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-global-cyber-usa-idUSKBN28Y1BF|author=Satter|date=December 24, 2020|first=Joseph Menn, Raphael|access-date=2021-03-03|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324055933/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-global-cyber-usa-idUSKBN28Y1BF|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="nyt-2020-12-24">{{Cite web|title=Russians Are Believed to Have Used Microsoft Resellers in Cyberattacks|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/24/us/russia-microsoft-resellers-cyberattacks.html|author=Perlroth|date=December 25, 2020|first=Nicole|access-date=2021-03-03|archive-date=2021-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210531152106/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/24/us/russia-microsoft-resellers-cyberattacks.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。SolarWinds作为微软云客户之一遭到入侵，随后其存在严重安全缺陷的软件发布基础设施遭到控制，其广泛应用于美国政府和工业部门的Orion软件被攻击者植入后门。入侵者利用植入Orion的后门成功窃取大量机密信息。<ref name="slate-2020-12-16">{{Cite web|title=What We Do and Don't Know About the Massive Federal Government Hack|url=https://slate.com/technology/2020/12/solarwinds-hack-commerce-treasury-breach.html|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Wolff|date=December 16, 2020|first=Josephine|work=Slate|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216210929/https://slate.com/technology/2020/12/solarwinds-hack-commerce-treasury-breach.html|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref>此外，微软和VMware产品中的缺陷允许攻击者非法访问电子邮件等文档或通过[[單一登入|单点登录]]完成统一身份认证。<ref name="intercept-2020-12-17">{{Cite web|title=Russian Hackers Have Been Inside Austin City Network for Months|url=https://theintercept.com/2020/12/17/russia-hack-austin-texas/|accessdate=December 18, 2020|author=Hvistendahl|date=December 17, 2020|first=Mara|work=The Intercept|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217234405/https://theintercept.com/2020/12/17/russia-hack-austin-texas/|archivedate=December 17, 2020}}</ref><ref name="cs-2020-09-21">{{Cite web|title=CISA orders agencies to quickly patch critical Netlogon bug|url=https://www.cyberscoop.com/cisa-netlogon-microsoft-vulnerability-emergency/|accessdate=December 18, 2020|date=September 21, 2020|work=CyberScoop|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030201359/https://www.cyberscoop.com/cisa-netlogon-microsoft-vulnerability-emergency/|archivedate=October 30, 2020}}</ref><ref name="sw-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=Group Behind SolarWinds Hack Bypassed MFA to Access Emails at US Think Tank|url=https://www.securityweek.com/group-behind-solarwinds-hack-bypassed-mfa-access-emails-us-think-tank|accessdate=December 17, 2020|work=SecurityWeek.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216144033/https://www.securityweek.com/group-behind-solarwinds-hack-bypassed-mfa-access-emails-us-think-tank|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="at-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds hackers have a clever way to bypass multi-factor authentication|url=https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2020/12/solarwinds-hackers-have-a-clever-way-to-bypass-multi-factor-authentication/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Goodin|date=December 15, 2020|first=Dan|work=Ars Technica|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216212004/https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2020/12/solarwinds-hackers-have-a-clever-way-to-bypass-multi-factor-authentication/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="zd-2020-12-18-federated">{{Cite web|title=NSA warns of federated login abuse for local-to-cloud attacks|url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/nsa-warns-of-federated-login-abuse-for-local-to-cloud-attacks/|accessdate=2020-12-19|author=Cimpanu|date=2020-12-18|first=Catalin|work=Zero Day|publisher=Ziff-Davis|archive-date=2021-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209152753/https://www.zdnet.com/article/nsa-warns-of-federated-login-abuse-for-local-to-cloud-attacks/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="reuters-2020-12-22">{{Cite web|title='Dozens of email accounts' were hacked at U.S. Treasury -Senator Wyden|url=https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-global-cyber-idUKKBN28V2XQ|author=Satter|date=December 22, 2020|first=Raphael|access-date=2021-03-03|archive-date=2020-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228134329/https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-global-cyber-idUKKBN28V2XQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>

