s/russia-hack-putin-trump-biden.html|title=Billions Spent on U.S. Defenses Failed to Detect Giant Russian Hack|first=David E.|author=Sanger|first2=Nicole|author2=Perlroth|first3=Julian E.|last3=Barnes|date=December 16, 2020|work=The New York Times|accessdate=December 16, 2020|archivedate=December 16, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216200710/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/16/us/politics/russia-hack-putin-trump-biden.html}}</ref>袭击被發現后，时任美国总统[[唐納·川普|唐纳德·特朗普]]沉默了几天，推文稱「假媒體總是優先質疑網路攻擊來自俄羅斯，卻不敢討論網攻可能來自中國。」有媒體解讀川普暗示中国（而不是俄罗斯）具有嫌疑，并表示“一切都在掌控之中”。<ref name="ap-2020-12-19">{{Cite web|title=Trump downplays Russia in first comments on hacking campaign|url=https://apnews.com/article/donald-trump-politics-mark-levin-coronavirus-pandemic-hacking-6080f156125a4a46edef2a6dcf826611|accessdate=2020-12-20|author=Colvin|date=2020-12-19|first=Jill|publisher=Associated Press|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223025027/https://apnews.com/article/donald-trump-politics-mark-levin-coronavirus-pandemic-hacking-6080f156125a4a46edef2a6dcf826611|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="cnn-2020-12-19">{{Cite web|title=Trump downplays massive cyber hack on government after Pompeo links attack to Russia|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/19/politics/pompeo-us-government-hack-russia/index.html|accessdate=19 December 2020|author=Stracqualursi|date=19 December 2020|first=Veronica|work=CNN|archive-date=2021-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513100934/https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/19/politics/pompeo-us-government-hack-russia/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>《路透社》2021年2月報導，5名知情人士透露，美國[[联邦调查局|聯邦調查局]]調查員發現，來自中國的黑客，利用SolarWinds軟體漏洞侵入美國政府電腦，黑客所用的電腦系統和入侵工具，與由政權支持的中國網絡間諜所部署的一樣。<ref name="REUTERS0202"/>

== 背景 ==
此次事件在唐纳德·特朗普总统任期的最后一年中持续了8到9个月。由于特朗普在2018年取消了网络安全协调员这一职位，在攻击发生时白宫没有相关专业人才。<ref name="slate-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=Trump Has Been Whining About Fake Fraud—and Ignoring a Real Cybersecurity Crisis|url=https://slate.com/news-and-politics/2020/12/solarwinds-trump-hack-fireeye.html|accessdate=December 16, 2020|author=Kaplan|date=December 15, 2020|first=Fred|work=Slate|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216060553/https://slate.com/news-and-politics/2020/12/solarwinds-trump-hack-fireeye.html|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="nyt-2018-05-15">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/05/15/technology/white-house-cybersecurity.html|title=White House Eliminates Cybersecurity Coordinator Role (Published 2018)|first=Nicole|author=Perlroth|first2=David E.|author2=Sanger|date=May 16, 2018|work=The New York Times|accessdate=December 16, 2020|archivedate=December 13, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213234429/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/05/15/technology/white-house-cybersecurity.html}}</ref>2020年12月13日，当此次攻击事件被曝光，负责协调此类事故应对的网络安全和基础设施安全局（CISA）也缺少一名通过[[美国参议院|参议院]]确认程序的局长<ref name="verge-2020-12-14">{{Cite web|title=Trump's chaos made America a sitting duck for cyberattacks|url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/12/14/22174429/solarwinds-hack-russia-cisa-christopher-krebs-cybersecurity-infrastructure|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Brandom|date=December 14, 2020|first=Russell|work=The Verge|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215170320/https://www.theverge.com/2020/12/14/22174429/solarwinds-hack-russia-cisa-christopher-krebs-cybersecurity-infrastructure|archivedate=December 15, 2020}}</ref>——2020年11月18日，这一美国国家网络安全机构的最高官员[[克里斯·克雷布斯|克里斯·克雷布斯]]被特朗普解雇。<ref name="indy">{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/us-treasury-hackers-breach-trump-russia-b1772639.html|title=Russian government hackers behind breach at US treasury and commerce departments|date=December 13, 2020|work=The Independent|accessdate=December 14, 2020|archivedate=December 13, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213233930/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/us-treasury-hackers-breach-trump-russia-b1772639.html}}</ref><ref name="Nakashima">{{Cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/trump-fires-dhs-election-official/2020/11/17/97d3fa5c-251c-11eb-952e-0c475972cfc0_story.html|title=Trump fires top DHS official who refuted his claims that the election was rigged|author=Nakashima|first=Ellen|author2=Miroff|first2=Nick|date=November 17, 2020|work=The Washington Post|accessdate=November 18, 2020|archivedate=November 18, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118041406/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/trump-fires-dhs-election-official/2020/11/17/97d3fa5c-251c-11eb-952e-0c475972cfc0_story.html}}</ref><ref name="hill">{{Cite web|title=Hackers backed by foreign government breach Treasury, Commerce departments: reports|url=https://thehill.com/policy/cybersecurity/530035-hackers-backed-by-foreign-government-breach-treasury-report|accessdate=December 15, 2020|author=Bowden|date=December 13, 2020|first=John|work=The Hill|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215005023/https://thehill.com/policy/cybersecurity/530035-hackers-backed-by-foreign-government-breach-treasury-report|archivedate=December 15, 2020}}</ref>与此同时，CISA的上级机构[[美国国土安全部|美国国土安全部]]（DHS）也缺少通过参议员确认程序的部长、副部长、总顾问、主管情报和分析的次长和负责管理的次长；与此同时，特朗普仍在逼迫CISA的副部长下台。<ref name="fn-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=Forensic News Roundup: Russia hacks U.S. government, Trump silent.|url=https://forensicnews.net/forensic-news-roundup-russia-hacks-u-s-government-trump-silent/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Cobb|date=December 15, 2020|first=Adrienne|work=Forensic News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062144/https://forensicnews.net/forensic-news-roundup-russia-hacks-u-s-government-trump-silent/|archivedate=December 18, 2020}}</ref><ref name="dhs-leadership">{{Cite web|title=Leadership|url=https://www.dhs.gov/leadership|accessdate=December 17, 2020|date=September 7, 2006|work=Department of Homeland Security|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216103017/https://www.dhs.gov/leadership|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="hill-2020-11-12">{{Cite web|title=Senior DHS cybersecurity official to step down at end of week|url=https://thehill.com/policy/cybersecurity/525721-senior-dhs-cybersecurity-official-to-step-down-at-end-of-week|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Miller|date=November 12, 2020|first=Maggie|work=The Hill|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128225021/https://thehill.com/policy/cybersecurity/525721-senior-dhs-cybersecurity-official-to-step-down-at-end-of-week|archivedate=November 28, 2020}}</ref>此外，[[美國政府問責署|美国政府问责署]]和其他机构提出的许多联邦网络安全建议也没有得到实施。<ref name="bloomberg-2021-01-13">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds Hack Followed Years of Warnings of Weak Cybersecurity|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-01-13/solarwinds-hack-followed-years-of-warnings-of-weak-cybersecurity|accessdate=2021-01-13|author=Sebenius|date=2021-01-13|first=Alyza|work=Bloomberg.com|archive-date=2021-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210517185430/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-01-13/solarwinds-hack-followed-years-of-warnings-of-weak-cybersecurity|dead-url=no}}</ref>

SolarWinds是一家总部位于[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]的美国政府网络监控服务承包商，在此次攻击之前其产品就已经曝出一些安全缺陷。<ref name="tp-2020-12-16">{{Cite web|title=The SolarWinds Perfect Storm: Default Password, Access Sales and More|url=https://threatpost.com/solarwinds-default-password-access-sales/162327/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|work=threatpost.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217143937/https://threatpost.com/solarwinds-default-password-access-sales/162327/|archivedate=December 17, 2020}}</ref>SolarWinds组织结构中没有设置首席信息安全官或网络安全高级主管。<ref name="nyt-2020-12-16">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/16/us/politics/russia-hack-putin-trump-biden.html|title=Billions Spent on U.S. Defenses Failed to Detect Giant Russian Hack|first=David E.|author=Sanger|first2=Nicole|author2=Perlroth|first3=Julian E.|last3=Barnes|date=December 16, 2020|work=The New York Times|accessdate=December 16, 2020|archivedate=December 16, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216200710/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/16/us/politics/russia-hack-putin-trump-biden.html}}</ref><ref name="bloomberg-2020-12-21">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds Adviser Warned of Lax Security Years Before Hack|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-21/solarwinds-adviser-warned-of-lax-security-years-before-hack|accessdate=December 22, 2020|date=December 21, 2020|archive-date=2021-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516053412/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-21/solarwinds-adviser-warned-of-lax-security-years-before-hack|dead-url=no}}</ref>早在2017年就有犯罪分子有偿提供SolarWinds基础设施的访问渠道。SolarWinds甚至建议用户在安装SolarWinds软件之前禁用[[反病毒软件|反病毒软件]]。2019年11月，一名安全研究人员警告SolarWinds，称他们的FTP服务器“任何黑客都可能上传恶意内容并将这些内容发送给SolarWinds的客户“。<ref name="krebs-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds Hack Could Affect 18K Customers|url=https://krebsonsecurity.com/2020/12/solarwinds-hack-could-affect-18k-customers/|accessdate=December 16, 2020|publisher=Krebs on Security|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216063419/https://krebsonsecurity.com/2020/12/solarwinds-hack-could-affect-18k-customers/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="itw-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds FTP credentials were leaking on GitHub in November 2019|url=https://www.itwire.com/security/solarwinds-ftp-credentials-were-leaking-on-github-in-november-2019.html|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Varghese|first=Sam|work=itwire.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215011307/https://itwire.com/security/solarwinds-ftp-credentials-were-leaking-on-github-in-november-2019.html|archivedate=December 15, 2020}}</ref><ref name="reuters-2020-12-16">{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/global-cyber-solarwinds/hackers-at-center-of-sprawling-spy-campaign-turned-solarwinds-dominance-against-it-idUSKBN28P2N8|title=Hackers used SolarWinds' dominance against it in sprawling spy campaign|date=December 16, 2020|accessdate=December 16, 2020|work=Reuters|language=en|archivedate=December 17, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217222405/https://www.reuters.com/article/global-cyber-solarwinds/hackers-at-center-of-sprawling-spy-campaign-turned-solarwinds-dominance-against-it-idUSKBN28P2N8}}</ref> 由于SolarWinds的Microsoft Office 365账户已经被入侵，黑客可以访问其电子邮箱，甚至可能可以访问一些文件。<ref name="reg-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds: Hey, only as many as 18,000 customers installed backdoored software linked to US govt hacks|url=https://www.theregister.com/2020/12/15/solar_winds_update/|accessdate=December 16, 2020|author=McCarthy|first=Kieren|work=The Register|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216222506/https://www.theregister.com/2020/12/15/solar_winds_update/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="reg-2020-12-16-github">{{Cite web|title=We're not saying this is how SolarWinds was backdoored, but its FTP password 'leaked on GitHub in plaintext'|url=https://www.theregister.com/2020/12/16/solarwinds_github_password/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Claburn|first=Thomas|work=The Register|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218002615/https://www.theregister.com/2020/12/16/solarwinds_github_password/|archivedate=December 18, 2020}}</ref>

2020年12月7日，也就是公开确认SolarWinds产品被用于大规模网络攻击的前几天，SolarWinds的前首席执行官凯文·汤普森退休。<ref name="cnbc-2020-12-16">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds hack has shaved 23% from software company's stock this week|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/12/16/solarwinds-hack-triggers-23percent-stock-haircut-this-week-so-far.html|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Novet|date=December 16, 2020|first=Jordan|publisher=CNBC|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216223540/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/12/16/solarwinds-hack-triggers-23percent-stock-haircut-this-week-so-far.html|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="reg-2020-12-16">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds' shares drop 22 per cent. But what's this? $286m in stock sales just before hack announced?|url=https://www.theregister.com/2020/12/16/solarwinds_stock_sale/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=McCarthy|first=Kieren|work=The Register|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217150244/https://www.theregister.com/2020/12/16/solarwinds_stock_sale/|archivedate=December 17, 2020}}</ref>当天，与该公司董事会有联系的两家私募股权公司抛售大量该公司股票。然而，被问及时这些公司否认进行[[內線交易|内幕交易]]。<ref name="mw-2020-12-16">{{Cite news|url=https://www.marketwatch.com/story/solarwinds-falls-under-scrutiny-after-hack-stock-sales-01608166019|title=SolarWinds falls under scrutiny after hack, stock sales|agency=Associated Press|work=MarketWatch|accessdate=December 17, 2020|archivedate=December 17, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217023156/https://www.marketwatch.com/story/solarwinds-falls-under-scrutiny-after-hack-stock-sales-01608166019}}</ref>

== 攻击方法 ==
此次事件的攻击者使用了多种攻击手段。<ref name="reuters-2020-12-17">{{Cite news|url=https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-usa-cyber-breach-idUKKBN28R3B7|title=Microsoft says it found malicious software in its systems|first=Joseph|author=Menn|date=December 18, 2020|work=Reuters|accessdate=December 18, 2020|archivedate=December 18, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062157/https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-usa-cyber-breach-idUKKBN28R3B7}}</ref><ref name="nyt-2020-12-17">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/17/us/politics/russia-cyber-hack-trump.html|title=More Hacking Attacks Found as Officials Warn of 'Grave Risk' to U.S. Government|first=David E.|author=Sanger|first2=Nicole|author2=Perlroth|date=December 17, 2020|work=The New York Times|accessdate=December 17, 2020|archivedate=December 17, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217202216/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/17/us/politics/russia-cyber-hack-trump.html}}</ref>

=== 微软漏洞利用 ===
攻击者利用了微软产品、服务和软件分销基础设施中的缺陷。<ref name="intercept-2020-12-17">{{Cite web|title=Russian Hackers Have Been Inside Austin City Network for Months|url=https://theintercept.com/2020/12/17/russia-hack-austin-texas/|accessdate=December 18, 2020|author=Hvistendahl|date=December 17, 2020|first=Mara|work=The Intercept|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217234405/https://theintercept.com/2020/12/17/russia-hack-austin-texas/|archivedate=December 17, 2020}}</ref><ref name="at-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds hackers have a clever way to bypass multi-factor authentication|url=https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2020/12/solarwinds-hackers-have-a-clever-way-to-bypass-multi-factor-authentication/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Goodin|date=December 15, 2020|first=Dan|work=Ars Technica|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216212004/https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2020/12/solarwinds-hackers-have-a-clever-way-to-bypass-multi-factor-authentication/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="reuters">{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-cyber-treasury-exclsuive-idUSKBN28N0PG|title=Suspected Russian hackers spied on U.S. Treasury emails – sources|first=Christopher|author=Bing|date=December 14, 2020|work=Reuters|accessdate=December 14, 2020|archivedate=December 14, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214025738/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-cyber-treasury-exclsuive-idUSKBN28N0PG}}</ref><ref name="nyt-2020-12-24"/>

至少有一家微软云服务分销商被攻击者入侵，这构成了一种供应链攻击，使得攻击者能够访问被入侵分销商客户使用的云服务。<ref name="wapo-2020-12-24"/><ref name="reuters-2020-12-24"/><ref name="nyt-2020-12-24"/>

除此之外，“Zerologon”漏洞（微软认证协议NetLogon中的一个漏洞）允许攻击者获取被入侵的微软网络中的所有用户名和密码。<ref name="intercept-2020-12-17">{{Cite web|title=Russian Hackers Have Been Inside Austin City Network for Months|url=https://theintercept.com/2020/12/17/russia-hack-austin-texas/|accessdate=December 18, 2020|author=Hvistendahl|date=December 17, 2020|first=Mara|work=The Intercept|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217234405/https://theintercept.com/2020/12/17/russia-hack-austin-texas/|archivedate=December 17, 2020}}</ref><ref name="cs-2020-09-21">{{Cite web|title=CISA orders agencies to quickly patch critical Netlogon bug|url=https://www.cyberscoop.com/cisa-netlogon-microsoft-vulnerability-emergency/|accessdate=December 18, 2020|date=September 21, 2020|work=CyberScoop|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030201359/https://www.cyberscoop.com/cisa-netlogon-microsoft-vulnerability-emergency/|archivedate=October 30, 2020}}</ref>这使得他们可以取得其他凭证来获取网络上其他合法用户的权限，帮助他们入侵Microsoft Office 365服务中的[[電子郵箱|电子邮箱]]。

此外，微软Outlook网页应用的一个缺陷可能允许攻击者绕过多重身份验证。<ref name="sw-2020-12-15"/><ref name="at-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds hackers have a clever way to bypass multi-factor authentication|url=https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2020/12/solarwinds-hackers-have-a-clever-way-to-bypass-multi-factor-authentication/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Goodin|date=December 15, 2020|first=Dan|work=Ars Technica|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216212004/https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2020/12/solarwinds-hackers-have-a-clever-way-to-bypass-multi-factor-authentication/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="schneier-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=How the SolarWinds Hackers Bypassed Duo's Multi-Factor Authentication – Schneier on Security|url=https://www.schneier.com/blog/archives/2020/12/how-the-solarwinds-hackers-bypassed-duo-multi-factor-authentication.html|accessdate=December 17, 2020|work=schneier.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217224933/https://www.schneier.com/blog/archives/2020/12/how-the-solarwinds-hackers-bypassed-duo-multi-factor-authentication.html|archivedate=December 17, 2020}}</ref>

此次事件中的攻击者入侵了[[Microsoft_Office_365|Microsoft Office 365]]，他们在长达几个月的时间里监控了美国国家电信资讯局（NTIA）和[[美国财政部|美国财政部]]工作人员的内部电子邮件。<ref name="reuters" /><ref name="indy">{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/us-treasury-hackers-breach-trump-russia-b1772639.html|title=Russian government hackers behind breach at US treasury and commerce departments|date=December 13, 2020|work=The Independent|accessdate=December 14, 2020|archivedate=December 13, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213233930/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/us-treasury-hackers-breach-trump-russia-b1772639.html}}</ref>他们的攻击显然使用了某种伪造的身份标记来绕过微软的认证系统。<ref name="gu">{{Cite web|title=US treasury hacked by foreign government group – report|url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2020/dec/13/us-treasury-hacked-group-backed-by-foreign-government-report|accessdate=December 14, 2020|date=December 13, 2020|work=The Guardian|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214030019/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2020/dec/13/us-treasury-hacked-group-backed-by-foreign-government-report|archivedate=December 14, 2020}}</ref><ref name="sky">{{Cite web|title=Foreign government hacked into US Treasury Department's emails – reports|url=https://news.sky.com/story/foreign-government-hacked-into-us-treasury-departments-emails-reports-12160763|accessdate=December 14, 2020|publisher=Sky News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214032244/https://news.sky.com/story/foreign-government-hacked-into-us-treasury-departments-emails-reports-12160763|archivedate=December 14, 2020}}</ref>单点登录功能的存在则增加了攻击的可行性。<ref name="reuters-2020-12-22"/>

=== SolarWinds漏洞利用 ===
攻击者也对SolarWinds使用了供应链攻击。<ref name="wired-2020-12-14">{{Cite web|title=No One Knows How Deep Russia's Hacking Rampage Goes|url=https://www.wired.com/story/russia-solarwinds-supply-chain-hack-commerce-treasury|accessdate=December 16, 2020|work=Wired|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217013054/https://www.wired.com/story/russia-solarwinds-supply-chain-hack-commerce-treasury/|archivedate=December 17, 2020}}</ref>攻击者可能通过已控制的SolarWindsde的Office 365帐户控制了其公司的软件构建系统。<ref name="at-2020-12-14">{{Cite web|title=~18,000 organizations downloaded backdoor planted by Cozy Bear hackers|url=https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2020/12/18000-organizations-downloaded-backdoor-planted-by-cozy-bear-hackers/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Goodin|date=December 14, 2020|first=Dan|work=Ars Technica|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216194610/https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2020/12/18000-organizations-downloaded-backdoor-planted-by-cozy-bear-hackers/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="tp-2020-12-16">{{Cite web|title=The SolarWinds Perfect Storm: Default Password, Access Sales and More|url=https://threatpost.com/solarwinds-default-password-access-sales/162327/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|work=threatpost.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217143937/https://threatpost.com/solarwinds-default-password-access-sales/162327/|archivedate=December 17, 2020}}</ref><ref name="reg-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds: Hey, only as many as 18,000 customers installed backdoored software linked to US govt hacks|url=https://www.theregister.com/2020/12/15/solar_winds_update/|accessdate=December 16, 2020|author=McCarthy|first=Kieren|work=The Register|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216222506/https://www.theregister.com/2020/12/15/solar_winds_update/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="reg-2020-12-16-github">{{Cite web|title=We're not saying this is how SolarWinds was backdoored, but its FTP password 'leaked on GitHub in plaintext'|url=https://www.theregister.com/2020/12/16/solarwinds_github_password/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Claburn|first=Thomas|work=The Register|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218002615/https://www.theregister.com/2020/12/16/solarwinds_github_password/|archivedate=December 18, 2020}}</ref>

2019年9月之前攻击者已经控制了SolarWinds的软件发布基础设施。<ref name="zd-2021-01-12">{{Cite web|title=Third malware strain discovered in SolarWinds supply chain attack|url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/third-malware-strain-discovered-in-solarwinds-supply-chain-attack/|accessdate=2021-01-13|author=Cimpanu|date=2021-01-12|first=Catalin|work=ZDNet|archive-date=2021-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318190718/https://www.zdnet.com/article/third-malware-strain-discovered-in-solarwinds-supply-chain-attack/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="wsj-2021-01-12">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds Discloses Earlier Evidence of Hack|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/solarwinds-discloses-earlier-evidence-of-hack-11610473937|accessdate=2021-01-13|author=Sebastian|date=2021-01-12|first=Dave|work=WSJ|archive-date=2021-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210607055202/https://www.wsj.com/articles/solarwinds-discloses-earlier-evidence-of-hack-11610473937|dead-url=no}}</ref>在构建系统中，攻击者修改了SolarWinds提供给网络监控软件Orion用户的软件更新。<ref name="reg-2020-12-20">{{Cite web|title=Trump administration says Russia behind SolarWinds hack. Trump himself begs to differ|url=https://www.theregister.com/2020/12/20/solarwinds_update_trump_contradicts_pompeo_russia_attribution/|author=Sharwood|first=Simon|work=The Register|access-date=2021-03-03|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201230341/https://www.theregister.com/2020/12/20/solarwinds_update_trump_contradicts_pompeo_russia_attribution/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="reg-2021-01-12-sunspot">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds malware was sneaked out of the firm's Orion build environment 6 months before anyone realised it was there – report|url=https://www.theregister.com/2021/01/12/solarwinds_tech_analysis_crowdstrike/|accessdate=2021-01-13|author=Corfield|date=2021-01-12|first=Gareth|work=The Register|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302073707/https://www.theregister.com/2021/01/12/solarwinds_tech_analysis_crowdstrike/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 首次已知非法修改作为攻击者的[[概念验证|概念验证]]（PoF）发生于2019年10月，这意味着他们已经取得了整个基础设施网络的控制权。

