work|archivedate=December 15, 2020}}</ref><ref name="reuters" /><ref name="bloomberg">{{Cite web|title=U.S. Government Agencies Hit by Hackers During Software Update|url=https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/politics/u-s-government-agencies-hit-by-hackers-during-software-update/ar-BB1bTMl4?fbclid=IwAR2jsg56Z2yz2pshs-3DmTZio5STK_0MHCWDliB8yr-VVAew-vvBpCgLqUE|accessdate=December 14, 2020|publisher=MSN|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062145/https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/politics/u-s-government-agencies-hit-by-hackers-during-software-update/ar-BB1bTMl4|archivedate=December 18, 2020}}</ref> 当用户安装更新，恶意程序将随之安装至受害者的系统。在休眠12-14天后该程序将开始尝试连接并加入攻击者的[[僵尸网络|僵尸网络]]。<ref name="zd-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=Microsoft and industry partners seize key domain used in SolarWinds hack|url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/microsoft-and-industry-partners-seize-key-domain-used-in-solarwinds-hack/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Cimpanu|first=Catalin|publisher=ZDNet|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217003334/https://www.zdnet.com/article/microsoft-and-industry-partners-seize-key-domain-used-in-solarwinds-hack/|archivedate=December 17, 2020}}</ref><ref name="tp-2020-12-14">{{Cite web|title=DHS Among Those Hit in Sophisticated Cyberattack by Foreign Adversaries – Report|url=https://threatpost.com/dhs-sophisticated-cyberattack-foreign-adversaries/162242/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|work=threatpost.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216200536/https://threatpost.com/dhs-sophisticated-cyberattack-foreign-adversaries/162242/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="indy-2020-12-16">{{Cite news|author=Timberg|first=Craig|author2=Nakashima|first2=Ellen|date=December 16, 2020|title=Russians outsmart US government hacker detection system — but Moscow denies involvement|work=The Independent|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-russia-hacking-cyber-security-b1774793.html|accessdate=December 16, 2016|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062145/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-russia-hacking-cyber-security-b1774793.html|archivedate=December 18, 2020}}</ref><ref name="bbc-2020-12-16">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds: Why the Sunburst hack is so serious|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-55321643|accessdate=December 18, 2020|date=December 16, 2020|publisher=BBC|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216221808/https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-55321643|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref>成功加入网络后，攻击者将获得对该系统的控制后门<ref name="bc-2020-12-16">{{Cite web|title=FireEye, Microsoft create kill switch for SolarWinds backdoor|url=https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/fireeye-microsoft-create-kill-switch-for-solarwinds-backdoor/|accessdate=December 18, 2020|work=BleepingComputer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217033942/https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/fireeye-microsoft-create-kill-switch-for-solarwinds-backdoor/|archivedate=December 17, 2020}}</ref>。攻击者巧妙地将恶意程序流量伪装成合法Solarwinds流量来掩盖其意图。<ref name="at-2020-12-14">{{Cite web|title=~18,000 organizations downloaded backdoor planted by Cozy Bear hackers|url=https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2020/12/18000-organizations-downloaded-backdoor-planted-by-cozy-bear-hackers/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Goodin|date=December 14, 2020|first=Dan|work=Ars Technica|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216194610/https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2020/12/18000-organizations-downloaded-backdoor-planted-by-cozy-bear-hackers/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="ts-2020-12-14">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds Orion and UNC2452 – Summary and Recommendations|url=https://www.trustedsec.com/blog/solarwinds-orion-and-unc2452-summary-and-recommendations/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|date=December 14, 2020|work=TrustedSec|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215232939/https://www.trustedsec.com/blog/solarwinds-orion-and-unc2452-summary-and-recommendations/|archivedate=December 15, 2020}}</ref>根据CDN服务商统计，起初几周访问攻击者僵尸网络的流量主要来自北美，随后拓展到南美、欧洲和亚洲。<ref name="cloudflare-2020-12-16">{{Cite web|title=Trend data on the SolarWinds Orion compromise|url=https://blog.cloudflare.com/solarwinds-orion-compromise-trend-data/|accessdate=December 16, 2020|date=December 16, 2020|work=The Cloudflare Blog|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216170227/https://blog.cloudflare.com/solarwinds-orion-compromise-trend-data/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref>

攻击者似乎只使用了高价值目标系统的后门程序，<ref name="zd-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=Microsoft and industry partners seize key domain used in SolarWinds hack|url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/microsoft-and-industry-partners-seize-key-domain-used-in-solarwinds-hack/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Cimpanu|first=Catalin|publisher=ZDNet|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217003334/https://www.zdnet.com/article/microsoft-and-industry-partners-seize-key-domain-used-in-solarwinds-hack/|archivedate=December 17, 2020}}</ref>一旦进入目标网络，攻击者就会安装Cobalt strike等工具来提升权限。<ref name="sc-2020-12-14">{{Cite web|title=After high profile hacks hit federal agencies, CISA demands drastic SolarWinds mitigation|url=https://www.scmagazine.com/home/security-news/apts-cyberespionage/disconnect-or-power-down-after-high-profile-hacks-cisa-demands-drastic-solarwinds-mitigation/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|date=December 14, 2020|work=SC Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215070401/https://www.scmagazine.com/home/security-news/apts-cyberespionage/disconnect-or-power-down-after-high-profile-hacks-cisa-demands-drastic-solarwinds-mitigation/|archivedate=December 15, 2020}}</ref><ref name="ts-2020-12-14">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds Orion and UNC2452 – Summary and Recommendations|url=https://www.trustedsec.com/blog/solarwinds-orion-and-unc2452-summary-and-recommendations/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|date=December 14, 2020|work=TrustedSec|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215232939/https://www.trustedsec.com/blog/solarwinds-orion-and-unc2452-summary-and-recommendations/|archivedate=December 15, 2020}}</ref><ref name="at-2020-12-14">{{Cite web|title=~18,000 organizations downloaded backdoor planted by Cozy Bear hackers|url=https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2020/12/18000-organizations-downloaded-backdoor-planted-by-cozy-bear-hackers/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Goodin|date=December 14, 2020|first=Dan|work=Ars Technica|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216194610/https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2020/12/18000-organizations-downloaded-backdoor-planted-by-cozy-bear-hackers/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="nyt-2020-12-14">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/14/us/politics/russia-hack-nsa-homeland-security-pentagon.html|title=Scope of Russian Hack Becomes Clear: Multiple U.S. Agencies Were Hit|first=David E.|author=Sanger|first2=Nicole|author2=Perlroth|first3=Eric|last3=Schmitt|date=December 15, 2020|work=The New York Times|accessdate=December 15, 2020|archivedate=December 18, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062201/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/14/us/politics/russia-hack-nsa-homeland-security-pentagon.html}}</ref>由于Orion作为一个可信的第三方应用程序连接到客户的Office 365帐户，攻击者可以获得访问电子邮件和其他机密文件的权限。<ref name="cc-2020-12-18">{{Cite web|title=Mitigating Cloud Supply-chain Risk: Office 365 and Azure Exploited in Massive U.S Government Hack|url=https://www.ciphercloud.com/mitigating-cloud-supply-chain-risk-office-365-and-azure-exploited-in-massive-u-s-government-hack/|accessdate=December 18, 2020|date=December 18, 2020|publisher=[[CipherCloud|CipherCloud]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062211/https://www.ciphercloud.com/mitigating-cloud-supply-chain-risk-office-365-and-azure-exploited-in-massive-u-s-government-hack/|archivedate=December 18, 2020}}</ref>这种权限使得他们能够在系统中寻找有效的SAML证书，并使用这些证书伪装成合法用户，使用其他本地或线上服务并加密转移他们感兴趣的数据。<ref name="abc57-2020-12-16">{{Cite web|title=Massive hack of US government launches search for answers as Russia named top suspect|url=https://abc57.com/news/massive-hack-of-us-government-launches-search-for-answers-as-russia-named-top-suspect|accessdate=December 17, 2020|work=ABC57|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062229/https://abc57.com/news/massive-hack-of-us-government-launches-search-for-answers-as-russia-named-top-suspect|archivedate=December 18, 2020}}</ref>一旦窃取到合法身份，关闭Orion便不再能够切断攻击者对目标的访问。<ref name="reuters-2020-12-14">{{Cite news|url=