=== VMware漏洞利用 ===
此次事件中的攻击者还利用了VMware Access和VMware身份管理器的漏洞。这些漏洞能帮助入侵者持久化入侵成果。<ref name="krebs-2020-12-18"/><ref name="bloomberg-2020-12-18-vmware">{{Cite web|title=VMware Falls on Report Its Software Led to SolarWinds Breach|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-18/vmware-falls-on-report-its-software-led-to-solarwinds-breach|accessdate=December 18, 2020|date=December 18, 2020|publisher=Bloomberg|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326140153/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-18/vmware-falls-on-report-its-software-led-to-solarwinds-breach|dead-url=no}}</ref>截至2020年12月18日，虽然已经确定SUNBURST木马足够帮助入侵者利用VMware的漏洞，但是攻击者是否使用过该漏洞仍旧不明。

== 发现 ==

=== 微软漏洞 ===
在2019年和2020年期间，网络安全公司Volexity发现一匿名智库的微软产品存在漏洞并遭到入侵者利用。<ref name="volexity-2020-12-14">{{Cite web|title=Dark Halo Leverages SolarWinds Compromise to Breach Organizations|url=https://www.volexity.com/blog/2020/12/14/dark-halo-leverages-solarwinds-compromise-to-breach-organizations/|publisher=Volexity|access-date=2021-03-03|archive-date=2021-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210531210132/https://www.volexity.com/blog/2020/12/14/dark-halo-leverages-solarwinds-compromise-to-breach-organizations/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="bloomberg-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=Hacking Spree by Suspected Russians Included U.S. Think Tank|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-15/hacking-spree-by-suspected-russians-included-u-s-think-tank|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Tarabay|date=December 15, 2020|first=Jamie|publisher=Bloomberg L.P.|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062232/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-15/hacking-spree-by-suspected-russians-included-u-s-think-tank|archivedate=December 18, 2020}}</ref><ref name="sw-2020-12-15"/>攻击者使用独特的方法利用了该组织Exchange控制面板中的一个漏洞绕过了[[多重要素驗證|多重身份验证]]。2020年6月至7月，Volexity发现SolarWinds Orion漏洞植入了木马。即：微软漏洞（攻击入口）和SolarWinds供应链攻击（攻击目标）可以被入侵者结合，用来实现目的。Volexity表示他们无法确认攻击者的身份。

同样在2020年，微软发现有攻击者试图使用微软Azure基础设施非法访问CrowdStrike的电子邮箱。由于CrowdStrike出于安全考虑不使用Office365处理邮件，这次攻击失败了。<ref name="cs-2020-12-24">{{Cite web|title=Microsoft alerts CrowdStrike of hackers' attempted break-in|url=https://www.cyberscoop.com/crowdstrike-solarwinds-targeted-microsoft/|date=December 24, 2020|work=CyberScoop|access-date=2021-03-03|archive-date=2021-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104121515/https://www.cyberscoop.com/crowdstrike-solarwinds-targeted-microsoft/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

另外，在2020年10月前后，微软威胁情报中心报告称，一个明显受到他国协助的攻击者利用微软NetLogon协议中的“ZeroLogon”漏洞进行攻击。<ref name="intercept-2020-12-17">{{Cite web|title=Russian Hackers Have Been Inside Austin City Network for Months|url=https://theintercept.com/2020/12/17/russia-hack-austin-texas/|accessdate=December 18, 2020|author=Hvistendahl|date=December 17, 2020|first=Mara|work=The Intercept|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217234405/https://theintercept.com/2020/12/17/russia-hack-austin-texas/|archivedate=December 17, 2020}}</ref><ref name="cs-2020-09-21">{{Cite web|title=CISA orders agencies to quickly patch critical Netlogon bug|url=https://www.cyberscoop.com/cisa-netlogon-microsoft-vulnerability-emergency/|accessdate=December 18, 2020|date=September 21, 2020|work=CyberScoop|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030201359/https://www.cyberscoop.com/cisa-netlogon-microsoft-vulnerability-emergency/|archivedate=October 30, 2020}}</ref>2020年10月22日，CISA收到报告并向各州、地方、区县政府发出警告，要求他们寻找自身网络是否有遭到入侵的迹象，并指示他们如果受到威胁就重建网络。<ref name="cisa-2020-10-22">{{Cite web|title=Russian State-Sponsored Advanced Persistent Threat Actor Compromises U.S. Government Targets|url=https://us-cert.cisa.gov/ncas/alerts/aa20-296a|publisher=CISA|access-date=2021-03-03|archive-date=2021-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210520172150/https://us-cert.cisa.gov/ncas/alerts/aa20-296a|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年12月，VirusTotal和The Intercept接连发现德州奥斯汀市政府遭到入侵迹象。

=== SolarWinds漏洞利用 ===
2020年12月8日，网络安全公司[[火眼|火眼]]（FireEye）称其使用的红方工具被它国政府支持的黑客组织窃取，其怀疑对象是[[對外情報局|俄罗斯对外情报局]]（SVR）。<ref name="toi">{{Cite web|title=Hackers backed by foreign government reportedly steal info from US Treasury|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/hackers-backed-by-foreign-government-reportedly-steal-info-from-us-treasury/|accessdate=December 14, 2020|work=The Times of Israel|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214031245/https://www.timesofisrael.com/hackers-backed-by-foreign-government-reportedly-steal-info-from-us-treasury/|archivedate=December 14, 2020}}</ref><ref name="nyt-2020-12-08">{{Cite news|author=Sanger|first=David E.|author2=Perlroth|first2=Nicole|date=December 8, 2020|title=FireEye, a Top Cybersecurity Firm, Says It Was Hacked by a Nation-State|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/08/technology/fireeye-hacked-russians.html|accessdate=December 15, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215184304/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/08/technology/fireeye-hacked-russians.html|archivedate=December 15, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=US cybersecurity firm FireEye says it was hacked by foreign government|url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2020/dec/08/fireeye-hack-cybersecurity-theft|accessdate=December 15, 2020|date=December 9, 2020|work=The Guardian|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216014233/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2020/dec/08/fireeye-hack-cybersecurity-theft|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="nbc">{{Cite web|title=Federal government breached by Russian hackers who targeted FireEye|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/russian-hackers-breach-u-s-government-effort-aimed-agencies-private-n1251057|accessdate=December 14, 2020|work=NBC News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214024737/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/russian-hackers-breach-u-s-government-effort-aimed-agencies-private-n1251057|archivedate=December 14, 2020}}</ref><ref name="wired-2020-12-08">{{Cite web|title=Russia's FireEye Hack Is a Statement—but Not a Catastrophe|url=https://www.wired.com/story/russia-fireeye-hack-statement-not-catastrophe/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|work=Wired|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216000225/https://www.wired.com/story/russia-fireeye-hack-statement-not-catastrophe/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref>火眼公司表示，在调查其自身遭到的入侵和工具盗窃案过程中，他们意外发现了SolarWinds供应链攻击。<ref name="nw-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=Suspected Russia SolarWinds hack exposed after FireEye cybersecurity firm found "backdoor"|url=https://www.newsweek.com/solarwinds-russia-hack-cyberattack-fireeye-software-malware-backdoor-cybersecurity-1554730|accessdate=December 16, 2020|date=December 15, 2020|work=Newsweek|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216043909/https://www.newsweek.com/solarwinds-russia-hack-cyberattack-fireeye-software-malware-backdoor-cybersecurity-1554730|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="fireeye-sunburst">{{Cite web|title=Highly Evasive Attacker Leverages SolarWinds Supply Chain to Compromise Multiple Global Victims With SUNBURST Backdoor|url=https://www.fireeye.com/blog/threat-research/2020/12/evasive-attacker-leverages-solarwinds-supply-chain-compromises-with-sunburst-backdoor.html|accessdate=December 15, 2020|date=December 13, 2020|work=FireEye|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215110129/https://www.fireeye.com/blog/threat-research/2020/12/evasive-attacker-leverages-solarwinds-supply-chain-compromises-with-sunburst-backdoor.html|archivedate=December 15, 2020}}</ref>

FireEye在发现入侵行为后将其报告给负责美国网络安全防护的美国国家安全局（NSA）。<ref name="nyt-2020-12-14">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/14/us/politics/russia-hack-nsa-homeland-security-pentagon.html|title=Scope of Russian Hack Becomes Clear: Multiple U.S. Agencies Were Hit|first=David E.|author=Sanger|first2=Nicole|author2=Perlroth|first3=Eric|last3=Schmitt|date=December 15, 2020|work=The New York Times|accessdate=December 15, 2020|archivedate=December 18, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062201/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/14/us/politics/russia-hack-nsa-homeland-security-pentagon.html}}</ref>在接获火眼报告前，NSA对入侵毫不知情，而NSA也是SolarWinds的客户。

几天后，也就是12月13日，财政部和商务部遭入侵被公开，消息人士称这与火眼系统遭到入侵相关。<ref name="reuters" /><ref name="nbc">{{Cite web|title=Federal government breached by Russian hackers who targeted FireEye|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/russian-hackers-breach-u-s-government-effort-aimed-agencies-private-n1251057|accessdate=December 14, 2020|work=NBC News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214024737/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/russian-hackers-breach-u-s-government-effort-aimed-agencies-private-n1251057|archivedate=December 14, 2020}}</ref>12月15日，火眼公司证实，攻击财政部等部门与火眼的介质均为植入SolarWinds Orion软件升级的木马程序。<ref name="krebs-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=SolarWinds Hack Could Affect 18K Customers|url=https://krebsonsecurity.com/2020/12/solarwinds-hack-could-affect-18k-customers/|accessdate=December 16, 2020|publisher=Krebs on Security|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216063419/https://krebsonsecurity.com/2020/12/solarwinds-hack-could-affect-18k-customers/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="gu-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=What you need to know about the biggest hack of the US government in years|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2020/dec/15/orion-hack-solar-winds-explained-us-treasury-commerce-department|accessdate=December 16, 2020|author=Paul|date=December 15, 2020|first=Kari|work=The Guardian|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216090102/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2020/dec/15/orion-hack-solar-winds-explained-us-treasury-commerce-department|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref>

安全部门把注意力转移到了Orion软件升级上。发现被感染的版本是发布于2020年3月至2020年6月间发布的2019.4至2020.2.1HF1。<ref name="zd-2020-12-16">{{Cite web|title=Microsoft to quarantine SolarWinds apps linked to recent hack|url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/microsoft-to-quarantine-solarwinds-apps-linked-to-recent-hack-starting-tomorrow/|accessdate=December 16, 2020|author=Cimpanu|first=Catalin|publisher=ZDNet|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217002642/https://www.zdnet.com/article/microsoft-to-quarantine-solarwinds-apps-linked-to-recent-hack-starting-tomorrow/|archivedate=December 17, 2020}}</ref><ref name="sc-2020-12-14">{{Cite web|title=After high profile hacks hit federal agencies, CISA demands drastic SolarWinds mitigation|url=https://www.scmagazine.com/home/security-news/apts-cyberespionage/disconnect-or-power-down-after-high-profile-hacks-cisa-demands-drastic-solarwinds-mitigation/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|date=December 14, 2020|work=SC Media|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215070401/https://www.scmagazine.com/home/security-news/apts-cyberespionage/disconnect-or-power-down-after-high-profile-hacks-cisa-demands-drastic-solarwinds-mitigation/|archivedate=December 15, 2020}}</ref>火眼将这款恶意软件命名为SUNBURST。<ref name="zdnet">{{Cite web|title=Microsoft, FireEye confirm SolarWinds supply chain attack|url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/microsoft-fireeye-confirm-solarwinds-supply-chain-attack/|accessdate=December 16, 2020|date=December 14, 2020|publisher=ZDNet|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216173348/https://www.zdnet.com/article/microsoft-fireeye-confirm-solarwinds-supply-chain-attack/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="di-2020-12-16">{{Cite web|title=Sunburst Trojan – What You Need to Know|url=https://www.deepinstinct.com/2020/12/16/sunburst-trojan-what-you-need-to-know/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|date=December 16, 2020|work=Deep Instinct|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062210/https://www.deepinstinct.com/2020/12/16/sunburst-trojan-what-you-need-to-know/|archivedate=December 18, 2020}}</ref>微软称之为Solorigate。<ref name="tp-2020-12-16">{{Cite web|title=The SolarWinds Perfect Storm: Default Password, Access Sales and More|url=https://threatpost.com/solarwinds-default-password-access-sales/162327/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|work=threatpost.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217143937/https://threatpost.com/solarwinds-default-password-access-sales/162327/|archivedate=December 17, 2020}}</ref>攻击者用来插入SUNBURST到Orion更新的工具后来被网络安全公司CrowdStrike分离，他们称之为SUNSPOT。<ref name="zd-2021-01-12"/><ref name="bc-2021-01-12">{{Cite web|title=New Sunspot malware found while investigating SolarWinds hack|url=https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/new-sunspot-malware-found-while-investigating-solarwinds-hack/|accessdate=2021-01-13|author=Gatlan|date=2021-01-12|first=Sergiu|work=BleepingComputer|archive-date=2021-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210529185400/https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/new-sunspot-malware-found-while-investigating-solarwinds-hack/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="reg-2021-01-12-sunspot"/><!-- 因文件已删，故注解: [[File:SUNBRUST_attack_process.jpg|缩略图]] -->

