ssian government spies are behind a broad hacking campaign that has breached U.S. agencies and a top cyber firm|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/russian-government-spies-are-behind-a-broad-hacking-campaign-that-has-breached-us-agencies-and-a-top-cyber-firm/2020/12/13/d5a53b88-3d7d-11eb-9453-fc36ba051781_story.html|accessdate=December 14, 2020|author=Nakashima|date=December 13, 2020|first=Ellen|work=The Washington Post|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213220635/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/russian-government-spies-are-behind-a-broad-hacking-campaign-that-has-breached-us-agencies-and-a-top-cyber-firm/2020/12/13/d5a53b88-3d7d-11eb-9453-fc36ba051781_story.html|archivedate=December 13, 2020}}</ref>FireEye将攻击者命名为UNC2452；事故应对公司Volexity称他们为“暗晕（Dark Halo）”。<ref name="at-2020-12-14">{{Cite web|title=~18,000 organizations downloaded backdoor planted by Cozy Bear hackers|url=https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2020/12/18000-organizations-downloaded-backdoor-planted-by-cozy-bear-hackers/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Goodin|date=December 14, 2020|first=Dan|work=Ars Technica|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216194610/https://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2020/12/18000-organizations-downloaded-backdoor-planted-by-cozy-bear-hackers/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="sw-2020-12-15"/><ref name="bloomberg-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=Hacking Spree by Suspected Russians Included U.S. Think Tank|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-15/hacking-spree-by-suspected-russians-included-u-s-think-tank|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Tarabay|date=December 15, 2020|first=Jamie|publisher=Bloomberg L.P.|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062232/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-15/hacking-spree-by-suspected-russians-included-u-s-think-tank|archivedate=December 18, 2020}}</ref>2020年12月23日，FireEye首席执行官表示，俄罗斯是最有可能的罪魁祸首，这些攻击的手法与SVR惯用方法“非常相似”。<ref name="ds-20