ive-russian-hack-effort-breached-dhs-state-department-and-nih|archivedate=December 15, 2020}}</ref><ref name="cnn-2020-12-16">{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/16/tech/solarwinds-orion-hack-explained/index.html|title=Why the US government hack is literally keeping security experts awake at night|first=Brian|author=Fung|publisher=CNN|accessdate=December 18, 2020|archivedate=December 17, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217062640/https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/16/tech/solarwinds-orion-hack-explained/index.html}}</ref>

SolarWinds表示，在其30万客户中，有33,000客户使用Orion。<ref name="nyt-2020-12-14">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/14/us/politics/russia-hack-nsa-homeland-security-pentagon.html|title=Scope of Russian Hack Becomes Clear: Multiple U.S. Agencies Were Hit|first=David E.|author=Sanger|first2=Nicole|author2=Perlroth|first3=Eric|last3=Schmitt|date=December 15, 2020|work=The New York Times|accessdate=December 15, 2020|archivedate=December 18, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062201/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/14/us/politics/russia-hack-nsa-homeland-security-pentagon.html}}</ref>其中，大约有18000名用户安装了被安插后门的版本。<ref name="reuters-2020-12-14">{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/global-cyber-idUSKBN28O1Z3|title=U.S. Homeland Security, thousands of businesses scramble after suspected Russian hack|first=Jack|author=Stubbs|first2=Raphael|author2=Satter|first3=Joseph|last3=Menn|date=December 15, 2020|work=Reuters|accessdate=December 15, 2020|archivedate=December 15, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215113854/https://www.reuters.com/article/global-cyber-idUSKBN28O1Z3}}</ref><ref name="zdnet-18000">{{Cite web|title=SEC filings: SolarWinds says 18,000 customers were impacted by recent hack|url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/sec-filings-solarwinds-says-18000-customers-are-impacted-by-recent-hack/|accessdate=December 15, 2020|author=Cimpanu|first=Catalin|publisher=ZDNet|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215101510/https://www.zdnet.com/article/sec-filings-solarwinds-says-18000-customers-are-impacted-by-recent-hack/|archivedate=December 15, 2020}}</ref>

