es.com/2020/12/16/us/politics/russia-hack-putin-trump-biden.html|title=Billions Spent on U.S. Defenses Failed to Detect Giant Russian Hack|first=David E.|author=Sanger|first2=Nicole|author2=Perlroth|first3=Julian E.|last3=Barnes|date=December 16, 2020|work=The New York Times|accessdate=December 16, 2020|archivedate=December 16, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216200710/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/16/us/politics/russia-hack-putin-trump-biden.html}}</ref><ref name="gu-2020-12-16">{{Cite web|title=Deep US institutional secrets may have been exposed in hack blamed on Russia|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2020/dec/16/us-institutional-secrets-exposed-hack-russia|accessdate=December 17, 2020|date=December 16, 2020|work=The Guardian|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217173005/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2020/dec/16/us-institutional-secrets-exposed-hack-russia|archivedate=December 17, 2020}}</ref>网络冲突专家、[[柏林洪堡大學|柏林洪堡大学]]教授托马斯·里德说：“被盗数据将有无数的用途”，他补充道：“所采集的数据量很可能是《[[月光迷宫|月光迷宫]]》中的数据量的许多倍，如果把数据打印出来堆到一起，会比[[華盛頓紀念碑|华盛顿纪念碑]]高得多。”

