2020年12月8日，在其他组织被攻破之前，FireEye公布了针对红队工具被盗的对策。<ref name="wired-2020-12-08">{{Cite web|title=Russia's FireEye Hack Is a Statement—but Not a Catastrophe|url=https://www.wired.com/story/russia-fireeye-hack-statement-not-catastrophe/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|work=Wired|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216000225/https://www.wired.com/story/russia-fireeye-hack-statement-not-catastrophe/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="fireeye-2020-12-08-countermeasures">{{Cite web|title=fireeye/red_team_tool_countermeasures|url=https://github.com/fireeye/red_team_tool_countermeasures|accessdate=December 17, 2020|work=GitHub|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216112625/https://github.com/fireeye/red_team_tool_countermeasures|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref>

2020年12月15日，微软宣布SUNBURST只影响使用Windows的计算机，从12月16日起相关恶意软件已加入到微软的数据库中，Microsoft Denfender将能够检测并隔离SUNBURST。<ref name="bc-2020-12-15">{{Cite web|title=Microsoft to quarantine compromised SolarWinds binaries tomorrow|url=https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/microsoft-to-quarantine-compromised-solarwinds-binaries-tomorrow/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|work=BleepingComputer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216154827/https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/microsoft-to-quarantine-compromised-solarwinds-binaries-tomorrow/|archivedate=December 16, 2020}}</ref><ref name="zd-2020-12-16-quarantine">{{Cite web|title=Microsoft to quarantine SolarWinds apps linked to recent hack|url=https://www.zdnet.com/index.php/category/2381/index.php/article/microsoft-to-quarantine-solarwinds-apps-linked-to-recent-hack-starting-tomorrow/|accessdate=December 17, 2020|author=Cimpanu|first=Catalin|publisher=ZDNet|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062252/https://www.zdnet.com/index.php/category/2381/index.php/article/microsoft-to-quarantine-solarwinds-apps-linked-to-recent-hack-starting-tomorrow/|archivedate=December 18, 2020}}</ref>

